After render, the useEffect([modelOpen]) in Dashbord runs â†’ calls refresh() again.

If modal closes (setModelOpen(false)) â†’ same effect, another refresh.

ğŸ“Œ Final Flow Summary

Dashbord renders â†’ initializes state and calls useContent.

JSX renders with contents = [].

After render:

useContentâ€™s useEffect runs â†’ fetch + interval.

Dashbordâ€™s useEffect runs â†’ fetch again.

